{"tid":863954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鬼佬吹奏港鐵］Thank You Hong Kong!","createTime":"2018-10-16T02:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T02:37:13.000Z","uid":79232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24f92fe04b8298ea23842beeb3272e0c9ea669e2","tid":863954,"uid":79232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"In Hong Kong, if the metro is delayed by more than 30 minutes, it is required to pay HK$1,000,000 to the government!!!<br />\n<br />\nThat's roughly USD$100k. For one 30 min delay! <br />\n<br />\nMaybe that's why trains are on time....99.9% of the time. This is how the world's best metro looks like. <br />\n<br />\nAnd maybe that's how every metro should look like.<br />\n<br />\nI hate going in metros, especoally in New York. But this one was a blast to shoot. <br />\n<br />\nINSTAGRAM: @NasDaily<br />\nGROUP: Nas Daily Global<br />\n<br />\nP.S - Next video upload is going to be on a different time zone! 10 AM Toronto time, because it's time for Canada! Thank you Hong Kong / Asia!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nasdaily/videos/562124390875147/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnasdaily%2Fvideos%2F562124390875147%2F&d=nE4dWvOceGSz5OMKEp7B1v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=90fd5cdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nasdaily/videos/562124390875147/</a>"},{"pid":"b0f317c2b81eb6db289b96ad31a83bb1c298c9f7","tid":863954,"uid":79232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/16/101142_48b6955ac6872709584ea548f1da6f62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2F101142_48b6955ac6872709584ea548f1da6f62.png&h=dc3a9c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/16/101144_a2a72b923242c2370056728019c8d93f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li